It was this-a-way. W. J. Bryan, 15; Andrew Jackson, 12; Jeff Davis, 9;
                        Abraham Lincoln, 8; Thomas Jefferson, 8; Moses, 6; Abraham, 15; John the
                        Baptist, 3; Daniel Boone, 2; William McKinley, I."

"You can," replied the countryman succintly;
                        "they'll be putting dinner on the table in a few
                        minutes."
